    "image_with_text_YYj4Vj": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_Hackpa": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Traditional",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_y9z6gp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>SOPHISTICATED. CHARM. HOMAGE TO YOUR HOME.</strong></p><p>The beauty is in the detail. Illustrate the unique history of your home and epitomise an era using quality, crafted pieces. Implement modern living technologies whilst upholding classic appeal.</p><p>A traditionally styled home exudes timeless elegance through classic design elements and balanced proportions. Interiors often showcase rich wood tones, ornate lighting, and formal layouts with distinct living and dining spaces. The colour palette typically combines neutral base tones with rich accents like burgundy and navy, creating a cohesive and serene environment. Decorative elements such as antique furniture, detailed fireplaces, and Persian rugs enhance traditional charm. </p><p>The fixtures and <a href=\"/collections/appliances\" title=\"Appliances\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">appliances</span></a> you choose for your home are vital in bringing together the style you imagine. For example, the Nostalgia tapware collection by <a href=\"/collections/phoenix\" title=\"Phoenix\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Phoenix Tapware</span></a> offers a beautiful traditional range of <a href=\"/collections/tapware-bathroom\" title=\"Bathroom Tapware\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">tapware</span></a> in various finishes that exude timeless elegance. <a href=\"/collections/freestanding-ovens\" title=\"Freestanding Ovens\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Upright cookers</span></a> by <a href=\"/collections/smeg\" title=\"Smeg\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Smeg</span></a> boast luxury and classic designs to complete your traditional home.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_xXfbxQ": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Shop the Traditional Style Collection",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/traditional"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_Hackpa",
        "text_y9z6gp",
        "button_xXfbxQ"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Traditional2.jpg",
