    "image_with_text_GVhcGz": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_znFX64": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Modern Minimalism",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_PRrf8f": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>CONTEMPORARY. TIMELESS. BESPOKE SIMPLICITY.</strong></p><p><strong><br/></strong>Design that stands the test of time. Incorporate deliberate, styled minimalism to your home with well-considered avant-garde fixtures and fittings. Create a broad appeal for your bathroom.</p><p>Minimalism in kitchen design emphasises simplicity, functionality, and clean aesthetics, think <a href=\"/collections/franke-tapware\" title=\"Franke Tapware\">Franke tapware</a>. This style features clean lines, simple shapes, and a neutral colour palette dominated by whites and greys to create a calm, spacious atmosphere. </p><p>In bathrooms, minimalism continues with sleek fixtures, natural light, neutral colours to maintain a bright and airy feel. Functional layouts with ample storage keep the space clutter-free, and open designs enhance the sense of simplicity and space.</p><p>Creating a minimalist home  fosters a calm, orderly environment that prioritises essential elements and promotes a sense of tranquility and spaciousness.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_kiNrEB": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Shop the Modern Minimalism Style Collection",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/modern-minimalism"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_znFX64",
        "text_PRrf8f",
        "button_kiNrEB"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Modern_Minimalism2.jpg",
        "height": "small",
        "desktop_image_width": "small",
