    "image_with_text_z9x9Jj": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_7xTyU4": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Hotel Inspired",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_P7YnDR": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>INDULGENT. VOGUE. 5 STAR AT HOME.</strong></p><p>Spoil yourself every day with an exclusive bathroom, impeccably styled to your taste. Place a strong emphasis on premium fittings and features to achieve a 5-star feeling in your home.</p><p>A hotel-inspired bathroom exudes luxury and sophistication, featuring high-quality materials such as marble, granite, and premium tiles. Elegant fixtures such as <a href=\"/collections/shower-heads\" title=\"Shower Heads\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">overhead showers</span></a>, <a href=\"/collections/freestanding\" title=\"Freestanding Baths\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">freestanding baths</span></a>, and sleek tapware in finishes like chrome or matte black enhance the hotel-like ambience. Pamper yourself with <a href=\"/collections/accessories-bathroom\" title=\"Accessories\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">bathroom accessories</span></a> such as plush towels, designer toiletries, and <a href=\"/collections/heated-towel-rail\" title=\"Heated Towel Rails\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">heated towel rails</span></a> and indulge in luxury in the comfort of your own home.</p><p>The neutral and calming colour palette, typically consisting of whites, greys, and beiges, creates a serene atmosphere. Luxury touches like large mirrors, double vanities, and free-standing bath fillers further elevate the experience. Every detail provides a relaxing and indulgent ambience, ensuring the bathroom offers a tranquil retreat similar to that of a high-end hotel.</p><p>The overall ambience of a kitchen that exudes a hotel-like ambience should be one of luxury and efficiency, where every element is designed to enhance the cooking and dining experience. By incorporating high-end materials, state-of-the-art kitchen appliances<span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">,</span> elegant <a href=\"/collections/sink-mixers-sink-tapware\" title=\"Sink Mixers\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">sink mixers</span></a>, and thoughtful design, the kitchen can become a statement of both style and comfort within your home.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_CVjxcm": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Shop the Hotel Inspired Style Collection",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/hotel-inspired"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_7xTyU4",
        "text_P7YnDR",
        "button_CVjxcm"
      ],
