    "image_with_text_tjw634": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_4DmpTT": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Nordic",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_H3VGVV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>BALANCE. INTUITIVE FEATURES. RESTRAINT & REFINEMENT.</strong></p><p>Nordic design in kitchens and bathrooms is characterised by simplicity, functionality, and a connection to nature. Have the confidence to pare back the design of your bathroom and let quality cabinetry and fittings tell the story. Create harmony between textures and materials to achieve Nordic finesse.</p><p>A Nordic-styled kitchen translates to clean lines, minimalism, and efficient storage solutions, with a focus on open shelving and <a href=\"/collections/integrated-appliances\" title=\"Integrated Appliances\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">integrated appliances</span></a>. Think streamlined elegance, where every element is carefully chosen to achieve minimalist form and ultimate function. The integrated appliances by Smeg are the perfect addition to any minimalist kitchen wanting to achieve this look.</p><p>Nordic bathroom design continues with minimalist fixtures, frameless shower screens, and the use of neutral colours to create a calming atmosphere. Natural materials like wood and stone are used to add warmth and texture, while efficient storage solutions and user-friendly layouts enhance functionality. </p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_XiEx3E": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Shop the Nordic Style Collection",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/nordic"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_4DmpTT",
