    "image_with_text_6zP8eg": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_tNBdFe": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Organic",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_KRHJVq": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>TEXTURE BLEND. CONTRAST. ECLECTIC MODERN.</strong></p><p>Organic design emphasises harmony with nature through natural materials like raw wood, stone, and sustainable finishes. Integrate a collection of materials together to create a unique, harmonious bathroom experience. Think stone, think timber, think steel or chrome cohesively working together. </p><p>Earthy colour palettes and natural light create a warm, inviting atmosphere, meanwhile incorporating indoor plants enhances the connection to nature. </p><p>Your kitchen, bathroom and laundry spaces should prioritise seamless indoor-outdoor connections and high-quality craftsmanship, promoting a tranquil and natural ambience. </p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_83G6Pk": {
