    "image_with_text_Y7ppJh": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_jAp8pM": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Coastal",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_VECiRH": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>LIGHT TIMBERS. SOFT TEXTURES. NATURAL LIGHT.</strong></p><p>Picture yourself at the beach, think of that feeling you want to create in your home. Use colours and textures that reflect the ocean, sand and sky. Think light timbers, subtle tiles and loads of natural light.</p><p>Incorporating the light and airy feeling of the beach into your bathroom can achieved through loads of natural light, neutral colours and beachside decor. In the bathroom, sandy-coloured towels, brushed nickel tapware and a light timber vanity set up the perfect coastal suite.</p><p>The goal of a coastal aesthetic is to bring that beach holiday feeling to your home in a modern and minimalist way. Your kitchen can reflect your coastal style through white granite sinks, integrated appliances and kitchen accessories like shopping boards and minimalist cookbooks!</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_673iG7": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Shop the Coastal Style Collection",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/coastal"
