    "image_with_text_tT4Dkr": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_EebTNp": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Hamptons",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_ifhy8G": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>LUXURY. INVITING. SOPHISTICATED. </strong></p><p>Inspired by the luxury, elegance, and highlight of grand living of the Hamptons. Find clean white fixtures, paired with marble bench tops and bold tapware features.</p><p>Emulating that Hamptons luxury feel we all love in your home is achieved through adding a sense of grandeur to your spaces. Think chandelier or pendant lighting, all-white shaker-style cabinetry and traditional tapware. Hampton-styled homes use colours like white, grey, navy blue and touches of brushed gold for added glamour. </p><p>To achieve the perfect Hamptons look, carefully selected fixtures and accessories are key. In your kitchen, a striking gold sink mixer and white butler sink make the perfect Hamptons combo and you can’t go wrong with a traditional basin mixer and white basin in your bathroom. </p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_VeaBeD": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Shop the Hamptons Style Collection",
